semble|semble,code search,semantic code search,semble search,token-efficient search,find code,code search mcp,agent code search,semble find-related,semble savings|Fast, accurate code search for AI agents using ~98% fewer tokens than grep+read. Index any local or remote repo in ~250ms (CPU only, no GPU/API key). Supports natural-language and symbol queries, semantic similar-code discovery via `find-related`, and MCP server integration for Claude Code, Codex, Cursor, and OpenCode. MCP: `claude mcp add semble -s user -- uvx --from "semble[mcp]" semble`. CLI: `pip install semble` or `uv tool install semble`. Skill: `npx skills add https://github.com/akillness/oh-my-skills --skill semble`|MinishLab/semble|MIT|latest